Homework 5

Kolin Newby
CSCI4229 Fall 2020

Display a basic scene with a light source showing different lighting angles of the scene.

Key bindings
  l          Toggles lighting
  m          Toggles light movement
  []         Lower/rise light
  p          Toggles ortogonal/perspective projection
  +/-        Change field of view of perspective
  a/A        Toggle axes
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit

***This assignment took me around 4 hours to complete***

Cited:
Code from ex13, given in class, was heavily referenced for the completion of this assignment
Info on glNormal() from khronos.org was also referenced for the completion of this assignment